sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User / face
    participant A as Agent loop
    participant P as LlmProvider
    participant G as Gate (hooks · allowlist · human)
    participant T as Tool
    U->>A: run(prompt)
    A-->>U: run_start · turn_start
    A->>P: stream(system, history, tools, maxTokens)
    P-->>A: thinking_delta* · text_delta* · tool_call* · usage · stop
    loop per tool call
        A->>G: pre_tool_use hook → allowlist → permission_request
        G-->>A: permission_decision
        A->>T: execute(input, ToolContext) — sandboxed
        T-->>A: output ("ERROR: ..." on failure)
        A-->>U: tool_result
        A->>G: post_tool_use hook (advisory)
    end
    A->>P: next turn with tool results (max 15 turns)
    A-->>U: run_end {stopReason}
